==Trivia==
* A comment was written by Mod John A, the main developer of Death to the Dorgeshuun, in the [[RuneScript]] code for Bob's dialogue during the quest, which states "Bob is a crazy racist!"{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/1345372952750141442|date=2 January 2021|archiveurl=https://archive.vn/SKlpT|archivedate=9 January 2021|quote=The developer's intention, in Death to the Dorgeshuun, was very clearly for Bob to be racist: [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Equ5aYYXIAADewy?format=png ]}}
*Bob's statement that he doesn't "serve their kind", in reference to the gnome child, may be a reference to Star Wars, in which a similar statement is made towards C-3PO by the bartender of the Mos Eisley Cantina.
*The painting inside Bob's Brilliant Axe's may be a reference to Bob Ross's "Distant Mountain's" painting, as the framing and subject are nearly identical.

